snippet.title: MELVIN IS ALIVE!
snippet.description:
Melvin IS BACK! 

After Chad Wild Clay made "SNEAKING INTO OUR HOUSE After Christmas and Spending 24 Hours Spying On Hackers", Vy Qwaint created "WE LOST... Project Zorgo Wins. Battle Royal vs Hackers for Safe House After Hiding Underground", and Daniel Gizmo uploaded "Can You Survive the Chaos Simulator? Spy Ninjas vs Moving Uhaul Truck Challenge!", the Spy Ninjas found Melvin PZ9 and he is ALIVE!! Melvin PZ9 is bacK!! At the safe house Regina Ginera, Vy Qwaint, Chad Wild Clay, and Daniel Gizmo cry and hug Melvin PZ9. To prove that Melvin PZ9 is one of the Spy Ninjas and not a Project Zorgo Hacker, he takes a lie detector test. Melvin explains how he had to escape the secret lair in the Project Zorgo Headquarters the black pyramid. Melvin PZ9 passes the lie detector test and receives secret Santa gifts from the Spy Ninjas. Daniel cries because he is so full of happy joy and love. He really missed his best friend and is glad that Melvin PZ9 is alive and back. We are the spy ninjas. Chad and Vy make welcome Melvin back to the Spy Ninjas safehouse after kicking the Project Zorgo hackers out! We are the Spy Ninjas!! Kick Bump!
